ing: 1 (8 ounce) package Dubliner Irish cheese, shredded
des: "Serve this Irish beer and cheese dip with pretzels for a tasty snack. You can use any Irish cheese you prefer if Dubliner isn't available to you."
ins: Place the cream cheese in the bowl of a food processor; pulse the cream cheese while adding the Guinness and Worcestershire sauce. Add the garlic and Dubliner cheese; process until smooth. Spoon the mixture into a serving bowl; cover. Chill in refrigerator overnight or 8 hours before serving.
